# Issue-PR linkage

Every feature PR must reference its issue.

Required behavior:

- PR description includes `Fixes #<id>` or `Refs #<id>`.
- Commit messages include `Refs #<id>` when applicable.
- Do not close issues without linked implementation evidence and completed acceptance checklist.

Use `issue-ship` skill when opening or finishing PRs.
